short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes the Twitter Logo to various Hololive logos.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Hololive has taken over Twitter! Inspired by Twitter ruining its own logo, this plugin changes the logo to different Hololive images! All members are included!

Use the plugin menu to change which image is displayed.
